@EBankingResilientProducerAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5210

### Health check (circuit breaker status)
GET {{EBankingResilientProducerAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transactions/health
Accept: application/json

### Producer metrics
GET {{EBankingResilientProducerAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transactions/metrics
Accept: application/json

### Create a single transaction (retry + DLQ)
POST {{EBankingResilientProducerAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "FR7630001000123456789",
  "toAccount": "FR7630001000987654321",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "type": 1,
  "description": "Virement mensuel loyer",
  "customerId": "CUST-001",
  "riskScore": 5
}

